column2: Report on residency training information (2011-2012), American Board of Emergency Medicine.
column4: Smith-Coggins R and Carius ML and Collier RE and Counselman FL and Kowalenko T and Marco CA and Muelleman RL and Korte RC
column6: The American Board of Emergency Medicine (ABEM) gathers extensive background information on emergency medicine residency training programs and the residents in those programs. We present the 2012 annual report on the status of US emergency medicine training programs.
